{"id":"steps-to-calories","slug":"steps-to-calories","name":"Steps to Calories Calculator","category":"health","icon":"👟","description":"Convert daily step count to estimated calories burned based on your weight.","tags":["steps","calories","pedometer","health"],"fields":[{"id":"steps","label":"Daily Steps","type":"number","defaultValue":10000},{"id":"weight","label":"Body Weight (kg)","type":"number","defaultValue":70},{"id":"caloriesBurned","label":"Calories Burned (kcal)","type":"computed","precision":1},{"id":"distanceKm","label":"Distance Walked (km)","type":"computed","precision":2},{"id":"distanceMiles","label":"Distance (miles)","type":"computed","precision":2},{"id":"activeMinutes","label":"Active Time (minutes, est.)","type":"computed","precision":0}],"groups":[{"id":"inputs","label":"Activity","fields":["steps","weight"]},{"id":"outputs","label":"Results","fields":["caloriesBurned","distanceKm","distanceMiles","activeMinutes"]}],"formulas":{"caloriesBurned":"steps * 0.04 * weight / 70","distanceKm":"steps * 0.000762","distanceMiles":"steps * 0.000762 / 1.60934","activeMinutes":"floor(steps / 100)"},"examples":[{"label":"10,000 steps, 70kg","inputs":{"steps":10000,"weight":70}},{"label":"15,000 steps, 80kg","inputs":{"steps":15000,"weight":80}}]}
